---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "ItemList",
  "name": "Telehealth Psychology Guides: Anxiety Sydney",
  "description": "Practical guides for people in Sydney looking for a telehealth psychologist for anxiety, covering costs, Medicare, evidence, waitlists, and how it all works.",
  "url": "https://sydneyanxietypsychology.com.au/guides/",
  "numberOfItems": 7,
  "itemListElement": [
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 1,
      "name": "What does a telehealth psychologist cost in Australia?",
      "url": "https://sydneyanxietypsychology.com.au/guides/cost-telehealth-psychologist-australia/"
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 2,
      "name": "How to choose a telehealth psychologist for anxiety",
      "url": "https://sydneyanxietypsychology.com.au/guides/how-to-choose-anxiety-psychologist-telehealth/"
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 3,
      "name": "Bulk billing for psychologists in Sydney",
      "url": "https://sydneyanxietypsychology.com.au/guides/bulk-billing-psychologist-sydney/"
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 4,
      "name": "Does online therapy work for anxiety?",
      "url": "https://sydneyanxietypsychology.com.au/guides/does-online-therapy-work-for-anxiety/"
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 5,
      "name": "How telehealth psychology works",
      "url": "https://sydneyanxietypsychology.com.au/guides/how-telehealth-psychology-works/"
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 6,
      "name": "Psychology waitlists in Sydney: what to know",
      "url": "https://sydneyanxietypsychology.com.au/guides/psychologist-waitlist-sydney/"
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 7,
      "name": "Clinical psychologist vs registered psychologist: what is the difference?",
      "url": "https://sydneyanxietypsychology.com.au/guides/clinical-psychologist-vs-registered-psychologist/"
    }
  ]
};
---
<Base
  title="Telehealth Psychology Guides | Sydney Anxiety Psychology"
  description="Practical guides for finding a telehealth psychologist for anxiety in Sydney: costs, Medicare rebates, evidence, waitlists, and how it all works."
  schema={schema}
>
  <div class="main-content">
    <div class="container">

      <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <a href="/">Home</a> &rsaquo; Guides
      </p>

      <h1>Telehealth Psychology Guides</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 2rem;">Practical information for people in Sydney considering, or working to access, a telehealth psychologist for anxiety. Straightforward coverage of costs, Medicare, evidence, and the referral process.</p>

      <div style="display: grid; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.15rem;"><a href="/guides/cost-telehealth-psychologist-australia/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">What does a telehealth psychologist cost in Australia?</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Clear breakdown of fees, Medicare rebates ($98.95 per session for a registered psychologist from 1 July 2025), and how to get a Mental Health Treatment Plan from your GP.</p>
          <a href="/guides/cost-telehealth-psychologist-australia/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the cost guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.15rem;"><a href="/guides/how-to-choose-anxiety-psychologist-telehealth/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">How to choose a telehealth psychologist for anxiety</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">What to look for in a psychologist: AHPRA registration, registered vs clinical explained plainly, therapy approaches (CBT, ACT, EMDR) in plain English, questions to ask before booking, and how to know if telehealth suits your situation.</p>
          <a href="/guides/how-to-choose-anxiety-psychologist-telehealth/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the choosing guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.15rem;"><a href="/guides/bulk-billing-psychologist-sydney/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">Bulk billing for psychologists in Sydney: what to expect</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Does bulk billing for psychologists exist in Sydney? Honest guide to what the Medicare rebate covers, why bulk billing is rare in private practice, and what genuinely low-cost options are available.</p>
          <a href="/guides/bulk-billing-psychologist-sydney/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the bulk billing guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.15rem;"><a href="/guides/does-online-therapy-work-for-anxiety/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">Does online therapy work for anxiety?</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">A review of what the research shows, including which anxiety presentations are well-suited to telehealth, when in-person may be preferable, and what to realistically expect.</p>
          <a href="/guides/does-online-therapy-work-for-anxiety/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the evidence guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.15rem;"><a href="/guides/how-telehealth-psychology-works/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">How telehealth psychology works</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">What happens in a session, what AHPRA registration actually means, confidentiality rules, and why there are no subscriptions or lock-in contracts.</p>
          <a href="/guides/how-telehealth-psychology-works/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the how-it-works guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.15rem;"><a href="/guides/psychologist-waitlist-sydney/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">Psychology waitlists in Sydney: what to know</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Why waitlists exist, how telehealth significantly expands your access to available practitioners, and practical steps to be seen sooner.</p>
          <a href="/guides/psychologist-waitlist-sydney/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the waitlist guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.15rem;"><a href="/guides/clinical-psychologist-vs-registered-psychologist/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">Clinical psychologist vs registered psychologist: what is the difference?</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Training differences, AHPRA endorsement, Medicare rebate amounts ($145.25 vs $98.95 from 1 July 2025), and which may suit your situation. Both are qualified to treat anxiety.</p>
          <a href="/guides/clinical-psychologist-vs-registered-psychologist/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the comparison guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="cta-block">
        <h3>Ready to find a telehealth psychologist for anxiety in Sydney?</h3>
        <p>Tell us what you are looking for and we will connect you with a registered psychologist who specialises in anxiety and offers telehealth. You will hear back within 1 business day.</p>
        <a href="/connect/" class="btn--cta plausible-event-name=Guides+Index+CTA+Click">
          Find a psychologist
        </a>
        <p class="cta-block__note">Free to use. We connect you. We do not provide clinical services.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
